---
// AuthorBio — about-the-author block for the foot of journal essays.
// Pulls double-duty: gives readers a who-am-I anchor, and sends an
// authoritative author-link signal to search engines and LLMs.
---
<aside class="awj-author" aria-label="About the author">
  <img
    src="/media/portrait/andy-portrait.jpg"
    alt="Andy Whyte, Founder and CEO of MEDDICC"
    class="awj-author__photo"
    loading="lazy"
    decoding="async"
    width="96"
    height="96"
  />
  <div class="awj-author__body">
    <p class="awj-author__heading">About the author</p>
    <p class="awj-author__name">
      <a href="/about/">Andy Whyte</a>
    </p>
    <p class="awj-author__bio">
      Founder and CEO of <a href="https://meddicc.com/" rel="noopener">MEDDICC</a> and
      author of the best-selling book <a href="/book/">MEDDICC: The ultimate guide to
      staying one step ahead in the complex sale</a> (100,000+ copies sold, 4.7&#x2605;).
      17 years in enterprise sales before founding MEDDICC in 2021.
      Writes the Andy Whyte Journal weekly.
    </p>
    <p class="awj-author__cta">
      <a href="/about/">Read Andy's full story</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <a href="/speaking/">Book Andy to speak</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .awj-author {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 96px 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
    align-items: start;
    padding: var(--sp-5) var(--sp-5);
    background: var(--awj-paper);
    background-image: url('/assets/textures/paper_white.png');
    background-size: cover;
    border: var(--border-hard);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--awj-black);
    margin: var(--sp-5) 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .awj-author {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--sp-3);
    }
  }
  .awj-author__photo {
    width: 96px;
    height: 96px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    border: 2px solid var(--awj-black);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.05);
  }
  .awj-author__body { min-width: 0; }
  .awj-author__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-2);
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }
  .awj-author__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 28px);
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-3);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .awj-author__name a { color: var(--awj-black); text-decoration: none; }
  .awj-author__name a:hover { background: var(--awj-yellow); }
  .awj-author__bio {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--awj-ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-3);
  }
  .awj-author__bio a {
    color: var(--awj-black);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1.5px;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .awj-author__bio a:hover { background: var(--awj-yellow); }
  .awj-author__cta {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .awj-author__cta a {
    color: var(--awj-black);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--awj-black);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }
  .awj-author__cta a:hover { color: var(--awj-blue); border-color: var(--awj-blue); }
</style>
